@MayoChristophe Hi! That is correct, make sure the batteries are packed separately and securely in your hand luggage in order to avoid them short circuit while flying. 
Kind regards,
Rebecka

@a_hawker100 Hello, please contact us on FB Messenger or live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R with your case ID and we can help you take a look at the handling status of your claim.

Best regards,
Anton.

@jhu1231232 Hej, det man kan prova i dessa fall är att byta webbläsare, kolla så att betalmedlet är öppet för onlineköp samt inaktivera VPN tillfälligt om man använder det.

Om problemet kvarstår kan du kontakta oss på FB Messeger eller livechatt för hjälp https://t.co/z4gOZASkIh

// Anton.

@field_trips_ Hello. In that case please call Baggage service support on the phone for assistance. https://t.co/We1FdD8x8k

Best regards,
Anton.

@curtismfoster Hello, we are sadly not able to look into individual cases here over Twitter. Please contact us on live chat and we can help you take a look at the possibilities for your travel voucher https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R

Best regards,
Anton.

@marcnoruega Hi, the general handling time for claims is 6-8 weeks but due to current circumstances our Customer Care are handling a lot of claims from the strike so handling times may be longer. They will contact you on email as soon as possible.

Best regards,
Anton.

@himynameisrbca @himynameisrbca Hi, to submit a claim, please contact our Customer Care department via this link:
https://t.co/cXegpq5E0e We apologize for any inconvenience.
Kind regards, Mikael

@jaymaikel @jaymaikel Hi, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. If you haven't reported your bag at the airport, please do so here: https://t.co/uHX1YFlavt You can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbzrxs
or call baggage service (Miami): https://t.co/ZV9bTNLSZs
Kind regards, Mikael.

@RoryEtherington Hi Rory,
I’m happy to hear that you had a good experience with us. We really appreciate you writing us, and I will gladly pass your feedback along.
Kind regards, Lena

@Rosscopawsome @Rosscopawsome Hi,
I am very sorry that you have to wait! We deal with all cases as fast as we can and will get back to you as soon as we have handled your case.
Kind regards, Lena

@MrMadsen Hej @MrMadsen,
Tack för att du kontaktar oss! Vänligen kontakta vår kundservice med din bokningsreferens så hjälper vi dig gärna. Vänligen se bifogad länk:
https://t.co/wGHhBoFvXh

@skgrb Hi, we do not provide a voucher during the time your luggage is delayed. You can apply for compensation after the luggage has been found here: https://t.co/6708vPIUZM 
Best regards,
Stina

@umangjain Hi, please contact us by chat or phone to look at this possibility. https://t.co/b3QIqPkF0R
Best regards, 
Stina

@MaisamDatoo Hi, please contact us by chat or phone to see if we can add this to your booking. https://t.co/b3QIqPkF0R
Best regards,
Stina

@Sandy_Grigelis @Sandy_Grigelis Hi, I am sorry to hear that. You need to arrange a damage report. Please contact Baggage Service to check if you can arrange that without returning to the airport https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
You can read more about it here: https://t.co/yaDBpcxdM2
Kind regards, Mikael

@amymcc22 @amymcc22 Hi, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. You can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU or call baggage service for more info: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
I would advice to delete the twitter with your private information: The PIR number.
Kind regards, Mikael

@josenaves @josenaves Hi, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. For more information, please contact baggage service: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

You can read more about delayed baggage on our website: https://t.co/KQdOdrH9TM
Kind regards, Mikael.

@JamesAllanAtmos @JamesAllanAtmos I'm sorry to hear your bag is delayed and that there's issues contacting Hamburg Baggage Service.
Our customer care department can't search for your bag, but please send them a message regarding your case https://t.co/xMt9zSrqJc
Kind regards, Mikael.

@Nina_Lalic @Nina_Lalic Hi, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. For more information, please contact the baggage service at the airport: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

You can read more about delayed baggage here: https://t.co/yaDBpcxdM2
Kind regards, Mikael.

@MozFreak Hello
We can not check status on claims via Twitter you need to contact our customer service via chat or phone for that https://t.co/Ec5v80W12W choose country and at the bottom "contact us" 
Kind regards /Anna

@MartinCox0155 Hello Martin
If you are having trouble with the connecting flight you contact staff at the airport and they can help you further.
Kind regards /Anna

@Vanessa63741792 Hi Vanessa
Contact us on phone or chat via https://t.co/Ec5v80W12W , choose country and at the bottom choose "contact us" and we can help you further.
Kind regards /Anna

@Martyn58358571 @Martyn58358571 Hi, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. If you haven't reported your bag at the airport, please do so here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 You can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
or call baggage service here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
Kind regards, Mikael.

@returnofserve Hello
It can happen that they are sold out if no youth tickets are showing , you are welcome to contact us by chat or phone https://t.co/Ec5v80W12W  choose country and at the bottom "contact us" and we can check availability.
Kind regards /Anna

@MozFreak Hi 
Customer care will reply on e-mail when the case is handled. For further questions contact us on chat with your case ID https://t.co/Ec5v80W12W choose country and at the bottom choose contact us and chat will be available. 
Kind regards /Anna

@island_41 Hi Piero
You can contact us by chat via https://t.co/Ec5v80W12W choose region and at the bottom choose contact us and the chat shows. Remember to have your case id for the claim and customer service will help you check status.
Kind regards /Anna

@KasperLadegaard @KasperLadegaard Hi, please try to clear your cache and cookies or try a different web browser.
If you use a VPN service, try set the location to a nearby VPN server or turn it off. If that doesn't help, contact us via our live chat and we will assist you.
Kind regards, Mikael

@AlanBaird Hi Alan!
if you are not able to download your boarding pass you can collect it at the airport, at the machine or at the check- in desk.
Kind regards, Lena

@lalolette @lalolette Hi, you can order a copy of a receipt for your flight from our website https://t.co/OsXlAZQYrZ
It's under the subject: "Booking related".
Kind regards, Mikael

@Goldflexonline Hi @Goldflexonline
Agreement reached and the strike is cancelled.
Kind regards, Lena

@ZXZCW199788 @ZXZCW199788 Hi, I can't check bookings via Twitter due to security rules, please contacting us via our live chat so we can look into it https://t.co/fxd6BsEJUx
I would recommend deleting this twitter due to private information: your PNR and ticket number.
Kind regards, Mikael

@JelenaZanko @JelenaZanko Hi, I'm sorry to hear her bag is delayed. I can't check the status in my system, that is handled by the baggage service at the airport. Please contact them: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
Here you can read about delayed baggage: https://t.co/yaDBpcxdM2
Kind regards, Mikael

@MirandaOakley3 Hello! We are truly sorry for the inconvenience! for help with your tickets, please contact our customer service. Our contact information can be found here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Warm regards,
Jenny

@peterjensen @peterjensen Hi, I'm afraid I don't have any information regarding that. If you would like to submit your feedback, please contact our Customer Care department via this link:
https://t.co/Ni77XOBAk2
Kind regards, Mikael.

@ShaunaLynnie Hi Shauna!
It sounds good. Wish you a nice weekend!
Kind regards, Lena
